---
import { ArrowUpRight } from "lucide-react";

import Logo from "./vectors/logo.astro";
---

<section class="mb-4 h-full w-full">
  <div class="flex flex-col-reverse justify-center md:flex-row xl:px-40">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:w-1/2">
      <picture>
        <source srcset="/one-way.png" media="(min-width: 768px)" />
        <img
          src="/one-way-responsive.png"
          alt="One Way Sign"
          class="mask-gradient mt-2"
        />
      </picture>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-4 mt-20 flex items-center justify-center md:w-1/2">
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <h2 class="mb-3">
          <Logo class="h-auto w-full" />
          <span class="mt-6 font-bold">Digital Creator</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-2">
          Somos un grupo colectivo encargado de llevar la chercha a otro nivel,
          de manera que usted, mi querida persona, disfrute este pequeño
          pedacito de nosotros.
        </p>
        <p>@3peso | @3pesotv</p>
        <div class="mt-8 max-w-72">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@3peso/videos"
            target="_blank"
            class="group relative isolation-auto z-10 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border-2 border-white bg-[#121212] px-4 py-2 text-lg text-white shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md before:absolute before:-left-full before:-z-10 before:aspect-square before:w-full before:rounded-full before:bg-white before:transition-all before:duration-300 hover:text-[#121212] before:hover:left-0 before:hover:w-full before:hover:scale-150 before:hover:duration-300 lg:font-semibold"
          >
            ¡Disfruta el último video!
            <ArrowUpRight
              className="size-5 rotate-45 justify-end text-gray-50 duration-100 ease-linear group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:text-[#121212]"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mask-gradient {
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(black 60%, transparent);
    mask-image: linear-gradient(black 60%, transparent);
  }
</style>
